text: Veronika Gotseva (; born 29 May 1993) is a Bulgarian footballer who plays as a forward for the Bulgaria women's national team. ==International career== Gotseva capped most recently for Bulgaria at senior level in a 0–6 friendly loss to Croatia on 14 June 2019. ==References== Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football forwards Category:Bulgarian women's footballers Category:Bulgaria women's international footballers Category:Bulgarian expatriate footballers Category:Bulgarian expatriate sportspeople in North Macedonia Category:Expatriate footballers in North Macedonia
